<P>A <HI>Pillar of Salt</HI> To Sea&s;on a Corrupt Age. A SERMON TO bring <HI>Lot</HI>'s <HI>Wife</HI> to Remembrance. Preach'd at the LECTURE <HI>in HINGHAM.</HI></P>
<P>By <HI>Ebenezer Gay,</HI> M. A.</P>
