<P><HI>I remembred thy Judgments of old, O Lord.</HI></P>
<BIBL>1 Cor. x. 11.</BIBL>
<P><HI>Now all the&s;e things happened to them for En&s;amples: and they are written for our Ad|monition upon whom the ends of the world are come.</HI></P>
